short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The inclusivity coach for your online meetings

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Are you committed to running an inclusive team? The Lex Google Meet extension provides real-time feedback on behaviors that make for an inclusive workplace. Get nudges when you could be doing more to include disengaged team members or when individuals are interrupted frequently, and run 1:1's more effectively using our suggested engagement questions.
